    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise</p>

<p> If \(\underline{r} = {@co1@}\underline{i} + {@co2@}\underline{j} - {@co3@}\underline{k}\), evaluate \(\underline{r}\) and \(\underline{r'} = \dfrac{d\underline{r}}{dt}\) when \(t = 1.\)</p>

<ol class="HELM_parts">
<li><p> \(\underline{r}(1) = \) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] \(\underline{i} \; +\) [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]] \(\underline{j} \; -\) [[input:ans3]] [[validation:ans3]] \(\underline{k}.\)&nbsp;[[feedback:prt1]]</p></li>

<li><p> \(\underline{r'}(1) =\) [[input:ans4]] [[validation:ans4]] \(\underline{i} \; +\) [[input:ans5]] [[validation:ans5]] \(\underline{j} \; +\) [[input:ans6]] [[validation:ans6]] \(\underline{k}.\)&nbsp;[[feedback:prt2]]</p></li>

</ol>]]></text>
		</questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<h4 class="HELM_solution">Solution</h4>
<p>We are given \(\underline{r} = {@co1@}\underline{i} + {@co2@}\underline{j} - {@co3@}\underline{k}\), and asked to evaluate \(\underline{r}\) and \(\underline{\dot{r}}\) at \(t = 1.\)<br></p>

<ol class="HELM_parts">

    <li>
        <p>\( \underline{r}(1) = {@cc1@}(1)^2\underline{i} \; + \; {@cc2@}(1)\underline{j} \; - {@cc3@}\underline{k} = {@ta1@}\underline{i} \; + \; {@ta2@}\underline{j} \; - {@ta3@}\underline{k}\). </p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <p>\( \underline{\dot{r}}(t)={@taa1@}t\underline{i} \; + \; {@taa[2]@}\underline{j}&nbsp;,\) so:</p>
        <p>\( \underline{\dot{r}}(1)= {@taa1@}(1)\underline{i} \; + \; {@taa[2]@}\underline{j} = {@taa1@}\underline{i} \; + \; {@taa[2]@}\underline{j}\).</p>
    </li>

</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
